---
---

<section
  class="mx-auto grid min-h-screen w-full max-w-[1180px] gap-12 bg-white px-6 py-10 text-[#0f1115] sm:px-10 lg:grid-cols-[280px_minmax(0,760px)] lg:justify-center lg:gap-20 lg:px-12 lg:py-20"
  aria-labelledby="profile-title"
>
  <aside class="lg:sticky lg:top-20 lg:h-fit">
    <img
      class="mb-8 size-28 rounded-full bg-[#f2f3f5] object-cover"
      src="/profile.svg"
      alt="秦駿太朗のプロフィール画像"
    />

    <p class="mb-3 text-[12px] font-medium uppercase leading-none tracking-[0.16em] text-[#8a8f98]">
      Profile
    </p>

    <h1 id="profile-title" class="text-[40px] font-extrabold leading-[1.05] tracking-normal">
      Hata Shuntaro
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-[250px] text-[13.5px] leading-[1.85] text-[#8a8f98]">
      徳島出身 | 18歳。フロントエンドとデザインの分野が得意です。
    </p>
  </aside>

  <section class="min-w-0" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
    <div class="mb-5">
      <h2 id="about-heading" class="text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.55] tracking-normal text-[#8a8f98]">
        All about me
      </h2>
      <p class="sr-only">自己紹介Webページ</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-6">
      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-white bg-[#e8f2fd] p-5 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-2">
        <span class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-[#4f7bff] text-[12px] font-semibold text-white">
          基
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">基本情報</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 grid gap-1 text-[13px] leading-[1.7] text-[#6e747d]">
          <li>名前：秦駿太朗</li>
          <li>年齢：18歳</li>
          <li>出身地：徳島県</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-white bg-[#fcebe6] p-5 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-2">
        <span class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-[#ff6719] text-[12px] font-semibold text-white">
          UI
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">得意分野</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-[1.7] text-[#6e747d]">
          見やすさと使いやすさを考えた画面作り。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-white bg-[#fff1e6] p-5 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-2">
        <span class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-[#ff6719] text-[12px] font-semibold text-white">
          好
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">好きなこと</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[12px] font-medium text-[#6e747d]">
          <li class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-1.5">ゲーム</li>
          <li class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-1.5">紅茶</li>
          <li class="rounded-full bg-white/80 px-3 py-1.5">ゴルフ</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-[#ecedef] bg-white p-6 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-4">
        <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-[#f2f3f5] px-3 py-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-[#6e747d]">
          自己PR
        </span>
        <p class="mt-8 max-w-[520px] text-[18px] font-semibold leading-[1.9] text-[#0f1115]">
          情報を整理して、伝わるWebページを作ります。
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-[560px] text-[13.5px] leading-[1.9] text-[#6e747d]">
          見た目だけでなく、どこを押せばよいか、情報が伝わりやすいかを意識して制作します。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-white bg-[#f2f3f5] p-5 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-2">
        <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-[#6e747d]">
          Tokushima
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">徳島県について</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-[1.8] text-[#6e747d]">
          阿波おどりや鳴門の渦潮が有名な自然豊かな場所です。海や山が近く、落ち着いた環境が魅力です。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] border border-[#ecedef] bg-white p-5 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(15,17,21,0.04)] md:col-span-3">
        <span class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-[#0f1115] text-[12px] font-semibold text-white">
          学
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">学習中</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-[1.8] text-[#6e747d]">
          HTMLとCSSの構造を理解しながら、表現の幅を広げています。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="rounded-[18px] bg-[#0f1115] p-5 text-white shadow-[0_14px_36px_rgba(15,17,21,0.12)] md:col-span-3">
        <span class="grid size-9 place-items-center rounded-lg bg-white text-[12px] font-semibold text-[#0f1115]">
          先
        </span>
        <h3 class="mt-8 text-[15px] font-semibold leading-[1.4]">これから</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[13px] leading-[1.8] text-white/70">
          UIデザインの知識を増やし、見る人にとって使いやすいサイトを作れるようになりたいです。
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</section>
